HEADWORD: lecherousness
<hw>lech"er*ous*ness</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>an inclination to excessive
indulgence in sexual activity; habitually developing a strong sexual
arousal.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lust, lustfulness, itch.</syn>⟦br⟧
